e-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></summary><div class=\"mobile-panel\"><a href=\"/contact\">Company</a><a href=\"/products/restaurant\">Platform</a><a href=\"/demo\">Resources</a><a href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a><a href=\"/signup\">Get started</a><a href=\"/login\">Log in</a><a href=\"/signup\">Start free</a></div></details></header></div><main><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"SoftwareApplication\",\"name\":\"Loglime Restaurant Apps\",\"applicationCategory\":\"BusinessApplication\",\"operatingSystem\":\"Web\",\"url\":\"http://localhost:3000/products/restaurant\",\"offers\":[{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"name\":\"Menu Starter\",\"price\":\"29\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\"},{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"name\":\"Ordering Growth\",\"price\":\"79\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\"}]}</script><section class=\"hero\"><div class=\"container hero-grid\"><div class=\"hero-copy\"><span class=\"badge\"><span class=\"badge-dot\"></span>Loglime Restaurant Apps</span><h1 class=\"display\">Customer-facing apps for modern restaurants.</h1><p class=\"sub\">Sell branded apps for digital menus, online ordering, table bookings, loyalty offers and customer updates.</p><div class=\"cta-row\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-lg\" href=\"/signup\">Get an app package</a><a class=\"btn btn-outline btn-lg\" href=\"/app/dashboard\">View sample app</a></div></div><div class=\"mock-window\" aria-label=\"Loglime restaurant app preview\"><div class=\"mock-chrome\"><div class=\"mock-dots\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div><div class=\"mock-url\">app.loglime.com / restaurant / ordering</div></div><div class=\"dashboard-preview\"><div class=\"preview-top\"><div><span class=\"eyebrow\">Brioche and Co.</span><h3 class=\"h3\">Customer app package</h3></div><span class=\"badge badge-coral\"><span class=\"badge-dot\"></span>Live menu</span></div><div class=\"preview-kpis\"><div class=\"preview-kpi\"><span>Online orders</span><strong>128</strong></div><div class=\"preview-kpi\"><span>Bookings</span><strong>42</strong></div><div class=\"preview-kpi\"><span>Repeat guests</span><strong>31%</strong></div></div><div class=\"grid-2\"><div class=\"card card-pad\" style=\"display:grid;gap:12px\"><div class=\"cta-row\" style=\"justify-content:space-between\"><strong>App modules</strong><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--coral)\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-utensils\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 2v7c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h4a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2\"></path><path d=\"M7 2v20\"></path><path d=\"M21 15V2a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v6c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h3Zm0 0v7\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"table-map\"><div class=\"table-pill busy\">Menu</div><div class=\"table-pill \">Order</div><div class=\"table-pill \">Book</div><div class=\"table-pill busy\">QR</div><div class=\"table-pill ready\">Deals</div><div class=\"table-pill \">Loyal</div><div class=\"table-pill busy\">Pickup</div><div class=\"table-pill \">Alerts</div></div></div><div class=\"card card-pad\" style=\"display:grid;gap:12px\"><div class=\"cta-row\" style=\"justify-content:space-between\"><strong>Customer actions</strong><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--teal)\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chef-hat\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M17 21a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-5.35c0-.457.316-.844.727-1.041a4 4 0 0 0-2.134-7.589 5 5 0 0 0-9.186 0 4 4 0 0 0-2.134 7.588c.411.198.727.585.727 1.041V20a1 1 0 0 0 1 1Z\"></path><path d=\"M6 17h12\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"order-stack\"><div class=\"order-chip\"><span><strong>#1042</strong> <!-- -->Family meal</span><span class=\"pill\">Paid</span></div><div class=\"order-chip\"><span><strong>#1043</strong> <!-- -->Table booking</span><span class=\"pill\">New</span></div><div class=\"order-chip\"><span><strong>#1044</strong> <!-- -->Loyalty offer</span><span class=\"pill\">Sent</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"grid-2\"><div class=\"order-chip\"><span class=\"cta-row\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--primary)\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg>Tonight&#x27;s offer ready</span></div><div class=\"order-chip\"><span class=\"cta-row\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--primary)\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-dollar-sign\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"2\" y2=\"22\"></line><path d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\"></path></svg>Menu update published</span></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"nex-section nex-section-white\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"nex-section-head center\"><span class=\"badge\"><span class=\"badge-dot\"></span>App modules</span><h2>Everything a restaurant needs to launch a customer app.</h2><p>Start with the product a restaurant understands first, then add more customer actions later.</p></div><div class=\"nex-product-grid\"><article class=\"nex-product-card nex-card-yellow\"><span class=\"nex-product-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-table2 lucide-table-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4m6-6h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v4M9 3v18m0 0h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9m0 0h18\"></path></svg></span><h3>Ordering app</h3><p>Customers order pickup, delivery or dine-in from a branded restaurant app.</p></article><article class=\"nex-product-card nex-card-cyan\"><span class=\"nex-product-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-square-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 8h10\"></path><path d=\"M7 12h10\"></path><path d=\"M7 16h10\"></path></svg></span><h3>Digital menu</h3><p>QR menu, categories, item prices, photos and availability.</p></article><article class=\"nex-product-card nex-card-peach\"><span class=\"nex-product-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chef-hat\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M17 21a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-5.35c0-.457.316-.844.727-1.041a4 4 0 0 0-2.134-7.589 5 5 0 0 0-9.186 0 4 4 0 0 0-2.134 7.588c.411.198.727.585.727 1.041V20a1 1 0 0 0 1 1Z\"></path><path d=\"M6 17h12\"></path></svg></span><h3>Booking app</h3><p>Table booking and reservation requests from restaurant guests.</p></article><article class=\"nex-product-card nex-card-purple\"><span class=\"nex-product-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></span><h3>Loyalty offers</h3><p>Promos, repeat-customer rewards and customer updates.</p></article><article class=\"nex-product-card nex-card-dark\"><span class=\"nex-product-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-column\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16\"></path><path d=\"M18 17V9\"></path><path d=\"M13 17V5\"></path><path d=\"M8 17v-3\"></path></svg></span><h3>App analytics</h3><p>Orders, top items, bookings and customer actions.</p></article><article class=\"nex-product-card nex-card-cyan\"><span class=\"nex-product-icon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg></span><h3>Launch support</h3><p>Brand, menu and customer flow setup for faster go-live.</p></article></div></div></section><section class=\"nex-section\" id=\"future-modules\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"nex-section-head center\"><span class=\"badge\"><span class=\"badge-dot\"></span>Growth modules</span><h2>Start with one restaurant app, then add more ways to sell.</h2><p>Keep future modules visible without making the first launch feel complicated.</p></div><div class=\"grid-4\"><article class=\"nex-soft-card\"><span class=\"badge badge-teal\"><span class=\"badge-dot\"></span>Coming later</span><h3>Loglime <!-- -->Bookings</h3><p>Reservation requests and table booking pages</p></article><article class=\"nex-soft-card\"><span class=\"badge badge-purple\"><span class=\"badge-dot\"></span>Coming later</span><h3>Loglime <!-- -->Loyalty</h3><p>Customer rewards and offer workflows</p></article><article class=\"nex-soft-card\"><span class=\"badge badge-amber\"><span class=\"badge-dot\"></span>Coming later</span><h3>Loglime <!-- -->Ordering</h3><p>Direct online ordering and pickup flow</p></article><article class=\"nex-soft-card\"><span class=\"badge badge-blue\"><span class=\"badge-dot\"></span>Coming later</span><h3>Loglime <!-- -->Analytics</h3><p>Restaurant app sales and customer insights</p></article></div></div></section><section class=\"nex-closer\"><div class=\"container\"><span class=\"nex-small-pill\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg> Launch</span><h2>Package the app, add the restaurant brand, and start selling direct customer actions.</h2><p>Loglime gives restaurants the app layer customers see, without forcing a POS replacement conversation.</p><div class=\"cta-row\" style=\"justify-content:center\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/demo\">Book a demo</a><a class=\"btn btn-outline\" href=\"/pricing\">View pricing</a></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--><footer class=\"site-footer\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"footer-grid\"><div class=\"footer-brand\"><a href=\"/\"><span class=\"brand\"><img alt=\"Loglime\" width=\"300\" height=\"78\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"brand-image\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fbrand%2Flogo-jade-cropped.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fbrand%2Flogo-jade-cropped.pn